sequenceDiagram
    participant KBS as Trustee KBS
    participant CM as cert-manager
    participant Job as init-data-gzipper<br/>(Ansible Job)
    participant SrcCM as imperative/<br/>initdata ConfigMap
    participant Kyv as Kyverno<br/>Propagation Policy
    participant WlCM as Workload Namespace<br/>initdata ConfigMap
    participant KyvInj as Kyverno<br/>Injection Policy
    participant Pod as Confidential Pod

    KBS->>CM: Request TLS certificate
    CM->>KBS: Issue self-signed cert
    Note over Job: Runs periodically
    Job->>KBS: Fetch TLS cert from secret
    Job->>Job: Render TOML templates<br/>(aa.toml, cdh.toml, policy.rego)
    Job->>Job: Gzip + base64 encode
    Job->>Job: Compute SHA-256 + PCR8
    Job->>SrcCM: Create/update ConfigMap<br/>with label coco.io/type=initdata

    Note over Kyv: Propagation Policy watches source ConfigMap
    Kyv->>SrcCM: Detect ConfigMap with label
    Kyv->>WlCM: Propagate to workload namespaces<br/>(synchronize: true)

    Note over Pod: User creates Pod with annotation<br/>coco.io/initdata-configmap: initdata
    Pod->>KyvInj: Admission request
    KyvInj->>WlCM: Read initdata ConfigMap
    KyvInj->>Pod: Inject cc_init_data annotation<br/>io.katacontainers.config.hypervisor.cc_init_data
    Pod->>Pod: Start with attestation config

    Note over KyvInj: autogen disabled - rollout restart<br/>required to pick up new initdata
